# ==============================================================================
# DEPRECATED: Frontend .env is no longer the primary config source.
#
# All environment variables are now managed from the ROOT .env file:
#   → ../.env  (relative to this directory)
#
# The root docker-compose.yml passes all VITE_* variables as build args.
# For local `npm run dev`, Vite reads VITE_* from this file.
# Recommendation: symlink to root .env or copy VITE_* variables.
# ==============================================================================

# To use: copy the VITE_* section from the root .env.example
# or create a symlink:   mklink .env ..\.env     (Windows)
#                         ln -sf ../.env .env    (Linux/Mac)